@startuml
title Book Visit - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Pet Owner" as Owner
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "visits-service\nVisitController" as Visits
participant "VisitService" as Service
participant "RemoteClientsFacade" as Remote
participant "customers-service" as Customers
participant "vets-service" as Vets
database "visits schema" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "workflow-service" as Workflow

Owner -> Web: Choose pet, vet, date/time, reason
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/visits
Gateway -> Visits: route with USER JWT
Visits -> Service: bookVisit(request, jwt)
Service -> Remote: load pet and owner snapshot
Remote -> Customers: GET pet/owner
Customers --> Remote: PetSummary, OwnerSummary
Service -> Remote: validate vet availability
Remote -> Vets: GET availability
Vets --> Remote: slot available
Service -> DB: insert Visit(status=SCHEDULED)
Service -> MQ: publish VisitScheduledEvent
Service -> Workflow: start visit workflow
Visits --> Web: VisitResponse
@enduml
